{"tid":1879272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署反對譚德塞","createTime":"2020-02-14T06:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T01:26:51.000Z","uid":305479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb826066451070a157e9952ddcbb1b3d2a54fc0b","tid":1879272,"uid":305479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general?recruiter=1042623406&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_medium=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=washarecopy_20174937_en-CA%3Av5&amp;recruited_by_id=de3cab70-4e11-11ea-ab9a-a5077c21da2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general%3Frecruiter%3D1042623406%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_campaign%3Dpsf_combo_share_message%26utm_medium%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dwasharecopy_20174937_en-CA%253Av5%26recruited_by_id%3Dde3cab70-4e11-11ea-ab9a-a5077c21da2f&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKRy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=d6f743e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general?recruiter=1042623406&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_medium=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=washarecopy_20174937_en-CA%3Av5&amp;recruited_by_id=de3cab70-4e11-11ea-ab9a-a5077c21da2f</a><br />\n<br />\n連署書上指出，譚德塞在1月23日時，拒絕將中國武漢肺炎列為「國際公共衛生緊急事件」，但事實上，此冠狀病毒至今並無治癒方式，且之後短短5天內，確診和死亡人數都增加逾10倍，比如確診數從800人陡增到超過1萬人，以及死亡人數超過350人等，這與譚德塞低估肺炎疫情有關，因此「我們強烈認為譚德塞不適合擔任WHO總幹事，呼籲譚德塞立即辭職」。"},{"pid":"262d4f7a0a0ba0a1b7d98b5c6d49bd40826c6d59","tid":1879272,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T01:26:51.000Z","msg":"我唔會"}]}